creator: HomeRenoGuru
descriptionHtml:
HomeRenoGuru.sg - Singapore's No. 1 renovation portal, has the highest number of interior designs and affordable home renovation packages from over 500 interior design firms for homeowners to review.

FREE renovation quotes are available upon request based on the house type and design theme.

FEATURES:

- Browse over 20,000 interior design inspirations available. Filter by design theme, house type or budget range.
- Search through the designs quickly with our new search feature
- Check out the ★ ratings given to each interior design firm
- Read genuine reviews and recommendations from fellow homeowners
- Be inspired by specially designed 3D drawings and tailored renovation packages of the newly TOP BTO/Condo launches
- Hundreds of Interior Designers for your choosing
- Stay up to date with the latest articles and events
